questions.prompt: Popular spinoffs of The Oprah Winfrey Show have included programs hosted by psychologist Dr. Phil McGraw, celebrity chef Rachael Ray, cardiothoracic surgeon Dr. Mehmet Oz, and what Chicago-based interior decorator?
